'''''Prelude to Rebellion'' 0''' was an online preview issue to [[Dark Horse Comics]]' comic series ''[[Star Wars: Republic]]''. It was written by [[Peet Janes]] and published exclusively on the [[StarWars.com|Official Star Wars website]] in [[Wikipedia:en:Macromedia Shockwave|Shockwave format]].

It was taken offline later because the file was broken and could not be restored. It was not reprinted in the [[Star Wars: Prelude to Rebellion (trade paperback)|''Star Wars: Prelude to Rebellion'' trade paperback]], and [[Dark Horse Comics]] editor [[Randy Stradley]] has said that the comic will never be printed. Despite this, ''Prelude to Rebellion 0'' was reprinted for the first time in ''[[Star Wars Legends Epic Collection: Rise of the Sith Vol. 2]]''.

